<div class="prose-content max-w-3xl">

  <p>Our practice serves patients in Leven and the surrounding Levenmouth area of Fife. We are based at Leven Health Centre, Victoria Road, Leven.</p>

  <h2>Areas we cover</h2>
  <p>We generally accept registrations from patients with postcodes in the KY8 area, including Leven, Buckhaven, Methil, and nearby communities. This list is a guide only — if you're not sure whether your address is within our area, please call us on <a href="tel:{{ site.phone | replace(' ', '') }}">{{ site.phone }}</a> and our team will check for you.</p>

  <h2>Levenmouth cluster practices</h2>
  <p>Scoonie Medical Practice is part of the Levenmouth GP cluster. If you are already registered with another GP practice within this cluster, we are unable to accept your registration — this is a Health Board agreement across all practices in the area.</p>

  <h2>Not in our area?</h2>
  <p>If you live outside our catchment area, you can use the <a href="https://www.nhsinform.scot/scotlands-service-directory/gp-practices" rel="noopener noreferrer">NHS Inform GP practice finder</a> to find a practice near your home.</p>

  <h2>Ready to register?</h2>
  <p>If you've confirmed you're in our area, head to our <a href="/new-patients/register/">registration page</a> to find out how to join.</p>

</div>
